{"id":941631471,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"4 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1682782310,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"204 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/941631471/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Prefix Common Array of Two Arrays","memory":"123.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int match(vector<int>& A, vector<int>& B, int low, int high) {\n        unordered_map<int, int> umap;\n        \n        for(int i = low; i <= high; i++) {\n            umap[A[i]]++;\n        }\n        int match = 0;\n        for(int i = low; i <= high; i++) {\n            if (umap.find(B[i]) != umap.end()) {\n                match++;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return match;\n    }\n    \n    \n    \n    vector<int> findThePrefixCommonArray(vector<int>& A, vector<int>& B) {\n        \n        vector<int> count;\n        \n        for (int i = 0; i < A.size(); i++) {\n            count.push_back(match(A, B, 0, i));\n        }\n        \n        return count;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-prefix-common-array-of-two-arrays","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
